 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 11: 在 2022 年折腾 Hexo 升级</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/hexo%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/hexo%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/</guid><description>NPM 依赖全过期，Hexo 停在 3.x，插件报错爬满屏。一个下午搞定升级。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Jul 2022 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 10: 我折腾过的 Hexo 主题——Chic 二次开发记录</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/hexochic%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/hexochic%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/</guid><description>为了一个顺眼的博客主题，我改了配色、汉化了页面、自定义了样式——那些还在用力气折腾的时光。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jun 2022 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 9: 产品架构那些事</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</guid><description>架构这个词听起来很技术。但产品经理理解架构的方式，可能跟工程师完全不同。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Sep 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 8: 数据分析那些事</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</guid><description>做产品前几年，我以为数据分析就是跑 SQL。后来发现，跑数据不重要，提对问题才重要。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Jul 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 7: 产品营销那些事</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%90%A5%E9%94%80%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%90%A5%E9%94%80%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</guid><description>产品经理不只管功能。市场和营销思维，是做产品时必须带上的另一副眼镜。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Jul 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 5: 产品企业那些事</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</guid><description>产品不是孤立存在的。企业文化和团队氛围，决定了你能做出什么样的产品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Jul 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 6: 用户转化那些事</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%BD%AC%E5%8C%96%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%BD%AC%E5%8C%96%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</guid><description>转化率低不是玄学。MECE 分析法帮我把用户流失拆成了可优化的环节。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Jul 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 4: 用户留存那些事</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E7%95%99%E5%AD%98%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E7%95%99%E5%AD%98%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</guid><description>日活在涨，用户却在流失。拉新的数字掩盖了留存的真相——这是我最开始做产品时学到的一课。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Jul 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 3: 用户注册那些事</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</guid><description>2016 年初入产品行当，我对注册的理解还停留在做个表单就行。后来被数据教做人。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Jul 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 2: 魔兽世界与产品设计</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E9%AD%94%E5%85%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/%E9%AD%94%E5%85%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/</guid><description>从艾泽拉斯的插件DIY出发，聊一个产品经理的自我修养。玩游戏不只是玩游戏。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Jul 2014 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>No. 1: 我的第一个博客——Hexo + GitHub 搭建记录</title><link>https://kakarrot.com/writing/hexogithub%E8%BD%BB%E9%87%8F%E7%BA%A7%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://kakarrot.com/writing/hexogithub%E8%BD%BB%E9%87%8F%E7%BA%A7%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</guid><description>2013 年，我从 WordPress 投向 Hexo。一个连 CSS 都不会写的人，用命令行搭出了自己的第一个博客。</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2013 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>